data.description: 4.5 % Assumable Loan. Beautiful Home located on a huge private enclosed lot that borders Green space. Great scenic mountain views. 55+ neighborhood. Low HOA. Double sided Fireplace separates two different living spaces. Vaulted ceilings, lighted decorative shelving. Kitchen has island, Banquette seating and plenty of storage. All bedrooms and entry have walk-in closets. Primary Bedroom has nice bay window. Primary bath with Dual Vanity included. Screened in Arizona Room perfect place to sit and have morning coffee.
